Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What we have been doing is creating a context in which to hold an understanding of the whole process of addiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.25,0:00:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And by the time we finish today, we'll see why the world has been relatively unsuccessful in handling the whole problem of addiction,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.46,0:00:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,with the exception, of course, of Alcoholics Anonymous, which has been the only successful approach thus far.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The purpose is to create a context, a way of holding, a way of understanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.98,0:00:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,because context is the most important thing in our life,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,because out of context comes meaning, and out of meaning comes value,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.16,0:00:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and out of value comes goals, and therefore it really directs our entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This kind of learning, which is not left brain learning,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.12,0:00:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the right brain learns by familiarity, by circling over the same material.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:00:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who's listening to it this year is not the same person who listened to it last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, to hear the material, you become a different person,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.34,0:01:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and so nobody will hear the same thing they heard last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll recapitulate some of the things we said last year, and then we'll extend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.75,0:01:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll extend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.12,0:01:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for the writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.40,0:01:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a typical doctor's writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We learned this at medical school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.81,0:01:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And if your writing is legible, then you flunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.33,0:01:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.63,0:01:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You get called into the dean's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.45,0:01:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is typical doctor's writing, and therefore I'll explain these terms
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,so that those of you who can't actually read it will hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In the center is the box, and a lot of my talks, people in DeVille,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of the former residents there refer to the box and where they are in the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.33,0:01:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the box is really the ego as understood in psychology.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the self with a small s.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.61,0:02:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lower mind, the common everyday mind with a small m.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The bottom of the box, we always start with the bottom of the box and work our way up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.85,0:02:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The bottom of the box is a state, is an energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In the center of the box, these are really energy fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And energy fields are impersonal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,An energy field is impersonal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Those of you who have studied or heard of geomancy realize
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that an energy field in nature is impersonal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, these energy fields have labels and names,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.56,0:02:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's just the name of that energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.42,0:02:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To the right of it is the emotion that comes out of that energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the far right is the process going on in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In the center, then, we have in the box these fields of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.21,0:03:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And beginning at the bottom, we have guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Guilt, which you'll notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that is a reversed energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Underneath the names of these various energy fields is an arrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,which I would hope would be in a different color,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but I forgot my pink chalk today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll notice that there's a direction to the energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.48,0:03:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and also there's a number which calibrates the relative energy of that energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting with death, calibrated at zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And this can be repeated by anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and it has been repeated by many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been proven and verified.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you start with death at zero,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you will end up with enlightenment at 600,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.55,0:03:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,what the world calls enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends beyond duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you start with death at zero,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you will end up with 600 as the top of the box,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond which identification with the small self,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the personal ego, is transcended.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,At the bottom of the box, then, preceding death,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.17,0:04:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,are two states, apathy and guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll notice that in the middle,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll notice that the energy field goes to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The direction of the energy field indicates something extremely important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All those energy fields below the level of courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a crucial level in the understanding of the addictions,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,all the energy fields below courage are reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All the levels below courage are reversed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're all levels of victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all levels of having sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So being close to death,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we see apathy calibrates at 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We see guilt calibrates at 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,These states preceding death, we notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:05:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,are accompanied by an emotional state of hopelessness,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of despondency, of despair, of depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you slip into guilt itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,self-hatred, the feeling of sin, worthlessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And out of that comes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the destruction due to the loss of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That state of apathy, hopelessness, despondency,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,which precedes death,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is a state in which the individual becomes de-energized.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They become de-energized
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,because the state right above it is dispirited.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The loss of the desire to live,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and because of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the loss of energy from the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,which the spirit, that which is life,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,pulls into us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So apathy is a state of great importance
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in the addictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a state of great importance in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably a third of the world lives in a state of apathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty percent, perhaps, of the world lives in a state of apathy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.46,0:06:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow will not be any better than today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The mothers in Ethiopia and Africa,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,places like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,stare, just stare blankly,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,watching the children's bellies swell up with starvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll notice that the look on their face
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of just staring off into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no hope that life is going to get any better tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, therefore, hopelessness
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,characterizes the state emotionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And in that state, a person is unable to help themself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopelessness means just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So a friend of mine was president of the Nassau County Bar Association,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and he died of starvation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,all alone in a rooming house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Starvation on a combination of alcohol and Librium.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't he call somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He knew thousands of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He was very well respected and well loved and well liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't he just call somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Because out of hopelessness, it means just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There being no hope, there, of course, would be no purpose to make a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is extremely important because when patients come in,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,when people come in in a state of hopelessness,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,into the villa,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,into the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,into the office,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,into our groups,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,into the influence of our energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because they cannot help themself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the only thing you can do is pour energy into them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the process over on the right hand side is loss of energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.13,0:07:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,then all you can do is pour energy into the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Reason and logic has no effect on a person in that state of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.26,0:07:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So the mother who has lost her child,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, got a telegram from the State Department,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.29,0:07:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that your son is missing in action,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly stops speaking, she sits in her rocking chair,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:07:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,she stares blankly out the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,rocks back and forth and stops eating,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and doesn't respond to people anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, when a telegram comes from the State Department that it was a mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,it was another man with a similar name and they say,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,mother, mother, it was all a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it wasn't really Richard at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So she just stares blankly out the window and rocks back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And they say, mother, didn't you hear what we said?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see, the state has already changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your state of consciousness has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And in this state, because there is changes in the brain enzymes,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,so over on the left we're going to have a column,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,we could have a blackboard about 30 feet long,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,in which we're going to integrate the entire cosmos and all of man's experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But having a blackboard of this length will do it serially.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So obviously you see there are brain enzyme changes,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and at this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,at the very bottom you have actually the release of a death hormone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:08:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the release of a death hormone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Above that, in a state higher than that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of course you have the depression of the brain's neurotransmitters,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the so-called catecholamines,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,such as serotonin and norepinephrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Those brain enzymes, which when they become depleted,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.56,0:09:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,throw a person into depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course this happens in the addictions,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,where first there is an overstimulation of those neurotransmitters,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and then with the withdrawal of the drug,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,especially a drug like cocaine,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,there is then a severe depression of the neurotransmitters,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore drugs that have an up-effect
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,will throw a person into a depression when you remove them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman does not respond to the message
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that her son was not killed in action,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,because she's no longer capable of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the only thing we can do for a person
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in this energy field is to pour energy into them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Pour energy into them
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,by our presence, by our caring for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:09:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,by our prayers for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,by the sheer presence of our own physical energy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and our caringness,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,because the person is unable to care for themself,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in an attempt to get them up to the next higher energy field called grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Grief, which calibrates at 50,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.02,0:10:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,has a lot more energy than apathy at 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.02,0:10:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Grief at 75 has a lot more energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And how is that energy expressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Through emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So we know that when the mother
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,rocking back and forth in the rocking chair
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly begins to cry,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,we know that she's getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an expression of emotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and grief has a certain biologic purpose in the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so that it summons forth some kind of a biologic response.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When the infant cries, it summons the mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A couple of months ago, I was sitting on my front porch
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and I heard this little squeaking sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Squeak, squeak, squeak, squeak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And my cat went over to a flower pot,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:10:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, was very curious about the flower pot,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and I lifted up the flower pot,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and here's this little toad underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hop, hop, out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd been trapped there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So this little toad, you see, in his grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,his little expression,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,summoned forth a great power from the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,namely me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to take the flower pot off him
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,with the help of the kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you see that little squeak,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,summoned forth the cat,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and the cat summoned forth me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and so therefore you see in operation
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the power, you see the power,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.94,0:11:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,because we say the energy fields are not personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So what the little toad was expressing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,was that energy field, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and that energy field summoned the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So there is power in grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In ordinary life, we experience grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in ordinary daily life, as regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So that grief relates to the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,just as fear, the energy field above it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,relates to the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We experience grief in the form of regret,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,having to do with loss,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the feeling of loss,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and it leads eventually into depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Depression leads then, if it gets worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,slips into despondency, into hopelessness,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and into the bottom of the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happened in grief is the person, we say,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,has become dispirited.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dispirited.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All of these are coming about,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.73,0:12:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,all of these are, we say,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,are accompanied by random changes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but all of them are coming about
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,because everything under the level of courage
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is based on the illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that happiness is something outside of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, grief is a reaction
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,then to that illusion that happiness is out there
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and that you have lost it somehow in your life
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,through that person, that relationship,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.21,0:12:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that money, that position, that title,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the loss of your hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,your youth, your vigor, whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,your potency, your Cadillac.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:13:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All the things that people put their stuff on
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,as being the source of their happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the loss of out there leads to the feeling of regret,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,loss, depression, and the dispirited state.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,These lower states, grief and apathy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,come from the failure to face the energy field above it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,which is fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear, again a reversed energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So 100 is a lot of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You think what you can do with the energy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,of fear, not with the emotion of fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but with the energy of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can run like hell with fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can establish the whole Maginot Line,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,which the French did
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,in preparing for the onset of the Germans in World War II.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear motivates, obviously, a huge amount of human behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and sells insurance policies
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and a good part of our economy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,of course, is based on fear and the defenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's a lot of energy in fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And what we try to teach people to do
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is how to use the energy of these fields,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but not the emotion itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How to use the energy constructively
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,coming out of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So all these energy fields have their upside
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and their downside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The upside and the downside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.67,0:14:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The upside of fear is how to use that energy constructively
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,because you can do yourself a great favor
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,if you know what to be afraid of in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.02,0:14:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,To be afraid of the addiction, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is sensible in as much as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In ordinary life,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.63,0:14:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,we experience the energy field of fear
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,as worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Worry, anxiety, panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So fear has to do with the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with anticipated consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with all kinds of projections.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And the process going on over here in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of deflation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So the animal, when it's afraid,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:14:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,shrinks and hides
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:15:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and tries to camouflage itself and be invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And we all remember that in class,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, in second grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody know how much is so-and-so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And everybody shrinks behind the person in front of them
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and tries to become invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is where we like to become invisible
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And the whole animal kingdom reflects that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in its magnificent camouflage
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in which the insects and the birds and the animals
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,look like tree bark and various things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,To become invisible and disappear from attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.88,0:15:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is the basis, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of the psychological mechanisms
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to disappear from the space,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to disappear yourself from the space
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,through denial and projection
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and ways to remove yourself from being there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Facing this energy field of fear
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is what prevents falling into depression and despondency.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.81,0:15:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So the way out of depression and despondency
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,for anyone is to face what is the underlying fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason you're depressed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,is because you're unwilling to face
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the fear underlying the depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear is much easier to handle
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.45,0:16:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,once you understand how to handle fear
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,than is depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Depression really, in a way, can't be handled
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,except to look at what was not faced
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,that will pull you out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute you look at what the fear is
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,underlying the depression,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,depression now disappears
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and instead you feel afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is the fear usually?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It usually takes the form of
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I have lost my happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The source.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have lost the source of my happiness forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see that under depression
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is the thought, the fantasy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the idea, and the emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.34,0:16:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So the woman is saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,without my son, life is now meaningless to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He was my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I based my life around my son
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and what he was in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And now my life has no meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have lost the source of meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and happiness in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.40,0:17:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So depression then comes from
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The fear almost always takes the form
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have lost the source of my happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How is fear handled?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we teach people how to handle fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.04,0:17:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very simple thing to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's surprisingly one of the easiest things to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Handling fear then is merely
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,handling the fear of the fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And the way you handle fear is by disassembling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking the fear away from the fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you're no longer afraid of fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it's really a nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When you disassemble it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and take it down to what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, fear is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,a feeling of dryness in the mouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe palpitations,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.36,0:17:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe some weakness in the legs,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,butterflies in the stomach,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,gastrointestinal discomfort,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ask yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, could I handle that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I let go resisting that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you do is you let go resisting
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're actually experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and stop labeling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.46,0:18:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You stop giving it any attention
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to what the thoughts are
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,because what kind of thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,do you think fear is going to put out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's going to put out your thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So instead, what you concentrate on
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is the sensations running through your body
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're asking yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,could you let go resisting them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.71,0:18:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And you just keep letting go resisting them
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and you find that there's nothing to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I let fear run one time for two weeks solid
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and when it left, I missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's like my pal by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just those sensations running through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And after the first few minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,or after the first hour or so,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,if you have really a big one that you're handling,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,letting run out,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll find that you go right on functioning
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and that the fearful feelings running through your body
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,are nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel fear running through you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,as a physical experience
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,which is quite tolerable
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's really nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's much easier to handle, frankly, than a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easier to handle with nausea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easier to handle with a broken toe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.25,0:18:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, all the things that you've handled in your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,fear is really nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you lose your fear of fear
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and are willing to handle fear as it comes up,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,then the world in a way can really no longer control you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's fear, isn't it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that really runs you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and that you're at the effect of so much in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So losing your fear of fear
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and just realizing what it is
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that is really a nothing to handle experientially.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because the thoughts are an elaboration
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's no truth in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And the only thing that you're really experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.85,0:19:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and you force the person to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's how you do it with physical symptoms as well
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's part of self-healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've done some tapes and things on self-healing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and how I healed many things within myself
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,was using that technique of stop labeling it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,stop calling it anything
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and go into radical truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, radically, what is it you're experiencing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Radically speaking, what is it you're experiencing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not experiencing fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Any more than you can experience
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,asthma or allergies or hay fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are all concepts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't experience hay fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't experience sinus trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't experience any of those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't experience an ulcer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, radically speaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,what is it you're experiencing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're experiencing a stuffy nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Even stuffiness you're not experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.52,0:20:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,any more than with an ulcer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The person says,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, I'm feeling an ulcer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not feeling an ulcer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you're actually feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're feeling a sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, all of us who do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,we just learned that the first day, didn't we,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,when we couldn't go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You had to cancel,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go to the bathroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.52,0:20:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's a panicky thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And instead, you had to concentrate
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,on the fact that what are you radically experiencing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.52,0:20:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're experiencing a pressure in the lower abdomen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, can you handle a little pressure in the lower abdomen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you can handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But you cannot handle a thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go to the bathroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's a panicsville.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:21:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the same, whether you can't handle asthma,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.97,0:21:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't handle any of these labels,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but what you can handle
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is the sensation,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and let go resisting the sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In my own personal experience of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,all of these physical things will disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,as you keep letting go resisting
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the physicality of the sensation of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and let go of the thoughts that go with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and we teach people how to handle fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.58,0:21:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is really a nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, one of the first benefits you get out of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the willingness to handle the fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is the letting go of the depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You come out of depression instantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,out of hopelessness instantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the instant you're willing to handle the fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But people are not willing to handle fear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.70,0:21:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,unless they feel there's a safe way to hold that fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore we're going to be talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,how to hold some of these experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the context out of which you're holding that fear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,is now that you are bigger than the fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:21:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the healer of that fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:22:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the one that is holding the field
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.70,0:22:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which that fear is now being held.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.70,0:22:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're not at the effect of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.70,0:22:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,See, you've summoned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.70,0:22:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the master now, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the difference between whether a dog is barking
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.90,0:22:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,against your will,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.90,0:22:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,or whether you invite the dog to bark.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.90,0:22:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that the best way to begin,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,from my point of view...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.93,0:22:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You move into the physical,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.03,0:22:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,because the mind in panic
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.03,0:22:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is like a computer going wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.03,0:22:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you push fear button,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.03,0:22:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,it has enough fear programs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.03,0:22:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that you could think nothing but fear thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.03,0:22:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the rest of your time on the planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.03,0:22:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and it would never run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.03,0:22:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, those fear thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.03,0:22:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,would have engendered
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.03,0:22:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,whole new banks of fear thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.03,0:22:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The collective consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.03,0:22:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the number of fear thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in the collective consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.03,0:22:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is probably infinite, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.03,0:22:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-perpetuating.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.03,0:22:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Every fearful thought
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.03,0:22:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,creates a whole new bank of...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, trying to handle the fear thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.03,0:22:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in my experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.03,0:23:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is not too successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.03,0:23:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you handle the actual sensation,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.03,0:23:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll come out of depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.03,0:23:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The instant you come out of depression,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.03,0:23:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're facing is
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,what you thought was the source of your happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.03,0:23:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that you think you have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, you're now facing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.03,0:23:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting right down to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.03,0:23:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting much closer to the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.03,0:23:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,which, of course, has a powerful effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.03,0:23:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In the addictions,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,we try to get people to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.54,0:23:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, they come in in apathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.54,0:23:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My situation is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.54,0:23:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My case is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.54,0:23:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, my case is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.54,0:23:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And AA is fine for you folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.54,0:23:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And NA is fine for you folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.54,0:23:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And OA is fine for you folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All that stuff is okay for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.54,0:23:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My case is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.54,0:23:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And how is it different?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.54,0:23:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My case is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.54,0:23:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My case is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.99,0:23:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,To move them up out of hopelessness into grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.99,0:23:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when you begin to see the cost of,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.99,0:23:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,not only addiction,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.99,0:23:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but any physical illness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.99,0:23:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,or any problem in your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.99,0:23:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the next reaction you get is grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.06,0:23:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you see the loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.06,0:23:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.06,0:24:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because grief is really about cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.06,0:24:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what the cost has been.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.06,0:24:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The price.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.06,0:24:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see what you've sold out
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.06,0:24:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and what you've let go of.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.06,0:24:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And so therefore you move up
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.06,0:24:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,into a regret and a grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.06,0:24:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the addictive field,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.06,0:24:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,people go into regret and grief
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.06,0:24:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,over the loss that has occurred already
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.06,0:24:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,in their life about addiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.06,0:24:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they move up to fear
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.41,0:24:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,because grief having handled the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.41,0:24:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear now, they extrapolate
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.41,0:24:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,what has happened in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.41,0:24:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And unless you're somewhat retarded,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.41,0:24:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,you begin to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.41,0:24:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that this is a progressive illness
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.41,0:24:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and that the losses of the past
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.41,0:24:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,are nothing compared to
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.41,0:24:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,what they are going to be in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.41,0:24:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So far, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.41,0:24:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,you've lost a part of your stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.41,0:24:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep on drinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.41,0:24:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,you will lose your entire stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.41,0:24:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That becomes rather clear to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.41,0:24:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And so therefore they go into fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.41,0:24:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You move people up from fear
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.95,0:24:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,into wanting something better for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.95,0:24:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,To move them to the next level,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.95,0:24:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that of desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.95,0:24:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy level of desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.14,0:25:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,which calibrates at 125,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.14,0:25:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,has a lot of power in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.14,0:25:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious to all of us
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.14,0:25:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that desire runs all of Madison Avenue,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.14,0:25:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole marketing,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.14,0:25:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole marketing schemes
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.14,0:25:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of the whole United States,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.14,0:25:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the basis of the economy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.14,0:25:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And desire and the wanting of something
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.14,0:25:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,can drive your entire lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.14,0:25:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a question in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.33,0:25:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The technique of it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.33,0:25:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't go into today
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.33,0:25:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,because it is all part of research
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.33,0:25:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.33,0:25:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll tell you a couple of easy ways
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.33,0:25:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and we will do one of them in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.33,0:25:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We ourselves will calibrate the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.33,0:25:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,of what we're talking about today in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.33,0:25:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll use a very simple method
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.33,0:25:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that anybody can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.33,0:25:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There are even faster,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.33,0:25:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,simpler ways, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.33,0:25:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But we ourselves will test out the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.33,0:25:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,of everything said today.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.33,0:25:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And I always say,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.33,0:25:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,never believe anything a speaker says
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.33,0:25:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,unless you have yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.42,0:25:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,investigated their integrity,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.42,0:25:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,their energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.42,0:26:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,their reversity,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.42,0:26:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and where they're at.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.42,0:26:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So everything that we say today,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.42,0:26:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,we will test out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.42,0:26:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And during the bill of lectures,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.42,0:26:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,we literally do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.42,0:26:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole class.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.42,0:26:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We test out the various propositions
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.42,0:26:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that we have presented during these talks
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.42,0:26:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and prove whether they're so or not so,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.42,0:26:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,especially the most critical ones
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.42,0:26:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because today we'll be talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.42,0:26:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,what people are actually addicted to,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.42,0:26:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,which is something that escapes the world thus far.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.97,0:26:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So fear, then, is a very useful thing
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.97,0:26:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,if you use out of the energy of fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.97,0:26:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the fear of the addiction,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.97,0:26:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,driving you into wanting this,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.97,0:26:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,something better for yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.97,0:26:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to desire something better for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.97,0:26:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So desire at 125,000,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.97,0:26:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a lot of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.97,0:26:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And we experience it in ordinary life
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.97,0:26:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,as wanting this,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.97,0:26:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, craving this,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.97,0:26:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the lust,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.97,0:26:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,lust in its generic widest meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.97,0:26:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the addictions,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.97,0:26:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,they eventually become obsession and compulsions.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.97,0:26:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Obsessions and compulsions,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.97,0:26:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in which the person is willing to sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.97,0:27:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and sell out everything
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.97,0:27:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in the name of that obsession and compulsion,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.97,0:27:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,including life itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.97,0:27:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,all that life entails.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.97,0:27:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.97,0:27:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the addiction will ask for your body,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.97,0:27:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.97,0:27:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you will give it your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.97,0:27:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the fact that even the physical body
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.97,0:27:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to go in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.97,0:27:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you will say,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.97,0:27:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,well, if it goes, it goes, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.97,0:27:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,piecemeal or in toto,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.97,0:27:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,because by then everything else is gone
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.97,0:27:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and the only thing you've got left is the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.97,0:27:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and so that's going to go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.97,0:27:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So the person in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.97,0:27:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is willing then to give up the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.97,0:27:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So we know you can't scare people
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.97,0:27:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the addictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.97,0:27:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't scare people saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.97,0:27:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,if you keep doing this,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.97,0:27:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.97,0:27:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean anything to the person,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.97,0:27:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,because they are quite willing to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.97,0:27:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,At a certain level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.97,0:27:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,they are willing to do everything
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.97,0:27:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to maintain that which they are seeking.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.58,0:27:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field of desire then,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.58,0:27:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to begin to want something better for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.58,0:27:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So out of hopelessness,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.58,0:27:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to move the person into grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.58,0:27:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and grief to face the fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.58,0:28:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the fear I will never be happy again,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.58,0:28:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,because in the addictions, obviously,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.58,0:28:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the source of your happiness is out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.58,0:28:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So to cut a person off from the addiction,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.58,0:28:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you then see why they go into grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.58,0:28:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,because they have just lost
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.58,0:28:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the source of their happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.58,0:28:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,To move up to fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.58,0:28:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to move up to desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.58,0:28:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,for wanting something to crave,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.58,0:28:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to really want something
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.58,0:28:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that is better for yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.58,0:28:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and move out of the grief and the fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.93,0:28:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and move up to anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.93,0:28:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can move a person up to anger,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.02,0:28:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,anger over what?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.02,0:28:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger over being victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.02,0:28:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger over being victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.02,0:28:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger over being powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.02,0:28:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger over what the cost has been.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.02,0:28:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger at how you've had to sell yourself out
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.02,0:28:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.02,0:28:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger at the sheer cost of survival,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.02,0:28:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the sheer cost that you've had to pay
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.02,0:28:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to maintain this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.02,0:28:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So we experience anger in ordinary life
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.41,0:28:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,as resentment, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.41,0:28:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In daily life, it's resentment,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.41,0:28:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course that intensifies
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.41,0:29:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to hatred and grudges,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.41,0:29:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,eventually killing and war.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.41,0:29:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing about desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.76,0:29:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the situation with desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.76,0:29:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the desire that addiction itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.76,0:29:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the process in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.76,0:29:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of entrapment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.98,0:29:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The person is trapped by the addiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.98,0:29:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're at the effect of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.98,0:29:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So if Madison Avenue can program you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.98,0:29:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,with a certain want,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.98,0:29:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a certain desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.98,0:29:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,then you are run by that,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.98,0:29:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and you then will put forth
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.98,0:29:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,your money, time, energy, and effort
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.98,0:29:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to get that which you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.98,0:29:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,which is usually based on
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.98,0:29:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't have what other people have,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.98,0:29:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,or they'll think you have B.O.,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.98,0:29:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,or they won't love you,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.98,0:29:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,or your hair won't swirl in the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.98,0:29:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and make men go crazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.98,0:29:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,or whatever the picture program
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.98,0:29:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,has gone into your unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.98,0:29:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To be at the effect of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.98,0:29:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to have that Cadillac
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.98,0:29:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to be happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.98,0:29:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,otherwise people will not respect you, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.98,0:29:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So whatever you're entrapped by then
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.98,0:29:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,runs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.98,0:30:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So from this level then,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.98,0:30:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the person is obviously run by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.98,0:30:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we get people to see that,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.98,0:30:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and a lot of times they will go
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.98,0:30:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,directly right into anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.98,0:30:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the good of anger is that
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.02,0:30:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,it has an energy fuel of 150.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.02,0:30:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of anger,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.02,0:30:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,not the emotion of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.02,0:30:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,which leads to destruction,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.02,0:30:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,destructive action,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.02,0:30:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but the energy of the anger
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.02,0:30:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,can now be used for constructive action.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.02,0:30:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So that anger over the cost,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.08,0:30:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,over what has been,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.08,0:30:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and move the person up to pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.08,0:30:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Pride at 175 is a lot of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.53,0:30:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's enough to run the entire
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.53,0:30:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,United States Marine Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.53,0:30:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Pride runs the whole clothing industry,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.94,0:30:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the cosmetics industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.94,0:30:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The pride in one's appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.94,0:30:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and leads you to getting all kinds of degrees
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.30,0:30:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and what pride does with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.30,0:30:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's some of the greatest things
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.30,0:30:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done out of pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.30,0:30:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,especially in adolescence.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.30,0:30:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.30,0:30:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What a girl might think about something,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.30,0:30:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and then what it led to,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.30,0:31:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,just to erase that from your collar
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.30,0:31:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,because she might have seen that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.30,0:31:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course all night
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.30,0:31:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you never even took your coat off,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.30,0:31:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so she never would have seen it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.30,0:31:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But the pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.30,0:31:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy then of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.30,0:31:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is enormous.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.30,0:31:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's used constructively,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.30,0:31:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not a great place to hang out in.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.30,0:31:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pride is not a great place to hang out in
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.30,0:31:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the defensive nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.30,0:31:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,because the process going on in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.30,0:31:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is really one of inflation.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.30,0:31:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And the downside of pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.55,0:31:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the upside of pride
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.55,0:31:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is to begin to move into self-care,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.55,0:31:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to care about yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.55,0:31:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and to do something about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.55,0:31:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to use that energy of anger
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.55,0:31:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,now in a constructive way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.55,0:31:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The downside of pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.55,0:31:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and of a great importance to pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.55,0:31:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.55,0:31:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in all fields,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.55,0:31:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but especially addiction,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.55,0:31:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is denial.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.55,0:31:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.55,0:31:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The downside of pride is denial,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.55,0:31:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and in its other forms,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.55,0:31:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,contempt,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.55,0:31:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and the defensiveness that goes with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.55,0:31:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So that denial kills a lot of people
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.62,0:31:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,in the addictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.62,0:31:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.62,0:31:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It kills them,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.62,0:31:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,it happened in my own family,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.62,0:32:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,in several of my family members,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.62,0:32:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,closest nuclear family in fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.62,0:32:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,where people would go to a meeting and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.62,0:32:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,well those people need that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.62,0:32:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to an AA meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.62,0:32:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,they say,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.62,0:32:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,well,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.62,0:32:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,they need that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.62,0:32:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.62,0:32:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's usually said,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.62,0:32:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,with sort of looking down the nose,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.62,0:32:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,contemptuous,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.62,0:32:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that those worms there,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.62,0:32:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,they need that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.62,0:32:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And a lot of people in our society
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.62,0:32:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,who don't understand self-help groups
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.62,0:32:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,or spiritually based self-healing
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.62,0:32:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,still have that attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.62,0:32:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you still need those meetings?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.62,0:32:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But because you understand what it's all about,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.62,0:32:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you laugh at it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.62,0:32:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,because you realize that they don't really get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.62,0:32:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but they're projecting this within them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.62,0:32:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This within themselves upon that,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.62,0:32:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.62,0:32:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's what they see there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.62,0:32:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So the whole problem with pride is defensiveness,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.62,0:32:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to be defensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.62,0:32:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that pride is useful then as a transition.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.62,0:32:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And even the Marine Corps appeals to pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.62,0:32:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but what they really move you up into is courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.74,0:32:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because prideful people are hard to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.10,0:33:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So pride is useful as a transition.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.10,0:33:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The difficulty is that the person's
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.10,0:33:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,unconsciousness is inflated.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.10,0:33:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So we say the person
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.10,0:33:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is too big for their boots,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.10,0:33:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, that they have a swelled head.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.96,0:33:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The inflation is,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.96,0:33:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.96,0:33:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the state right below that, anger,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.96,0:33:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of expansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.96,0:33:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is one of inflation.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.96,0:33:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In anger, the process is one to become expanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.96,0:33:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So the animal that is in anger,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.96,0:33:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,its hair stands on end and its tail swells
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.96,0:33:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and it looks fierce and it expands itself
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.96,0:33:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to make itself a formidable opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.96,0:33:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So the person in anger,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.96,0:33:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,their veins swell out and they swell out
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.96,0:33:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and take up a lot of energy space
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.96,0:33:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to try and impose on you and scare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.96,0:33:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Boo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.96,0:33:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The anger then is an expanded state.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.96,0:33:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But pride is an inflated state,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.96,0:33:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,which is somewhat beyond that
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.96,0:33:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and has its own characteristics,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.96,0:33:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,particularly that of denial.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.96,0:33:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So we hear out of that coming contempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.96,0:34:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And the contempt for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.96,0:34:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly what a person needs,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.96,0:34:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly what the person needs
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.96,0:34:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is exactly what they have the contempt for
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.96,0:34:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're unable to handle that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.96,0:34:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,because out of pridefulness,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.96,0:34:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,there is the inability to accept one's limitations
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.96,0:34:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore they have to be projected
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.96,0:34:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and ridiculed in others.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.96,0:34:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So we try to move people in the addictions
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.28,0:34:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,through pride to use the upside of pride
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.28,0:34:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to move into constructive action
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.28,0:34:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and really to move the people up
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.28,0:34:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,into the level of courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.28,0:34:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Courage is a critical element
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.66,0:34:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to a level.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.66,0:34:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, we see when we calibrate it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.66,0:34:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that the energy field has jumped to 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.86,0:34:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,200 is a lot of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.86,0:34:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,An energy field of 200 is enough
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.86,0:34:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to settle the United States of America
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.86,0:34:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and settle the West,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.86,0:34:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to create all the industries,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.86,0:34:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to create all the empires,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.86,0:34:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to energize all of science.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.86,0:34:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Curiosity plus courage is enough
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.86,0:34:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to handle the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.86,0:34:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's an enormous energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.86,0:35:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it have so much energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.86,0:35:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It has that much energy
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.86,0:35:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,because you'll see by the arrows,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.86,0:35:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas these energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.86,0:35:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,were all reversed to the left,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.86,0:35:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the needle now goes to the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.86,0:35:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the level of courage then,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.86,0:35:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy field has shifted
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.86,0:35:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,from destructive to neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.86,0:35:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field is like an antenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.17,0:35:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can picture it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.17,0:35:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,because all things in the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.17,0:35:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,give off a vibration, an energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.17,0:35:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,at a certain frequency,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.42,0:35:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,which is unique to that individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.42,0:35:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything in the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.55,0:35:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,gives off an energy and a vibration.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.55,0:35:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And the track of that energy
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.55,0:35:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and that vibration is there forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.22,0:35:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field here is like an antenna,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.22,0:35:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,so that here it's like the antenna
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.22,0:35:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is set to negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.22,0:35:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is like a negative antenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.22,0:35:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The negative antenna pulls to it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.22,0:35:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,all that is destructive from the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.22,0:36:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we see at the bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.22,0:36:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the process is one of destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.22,0:36:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.29,0:36:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,destruction has finally succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.99,0:36:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an impersonal effect
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.99,0:36:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of the energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.15,0:36:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The person,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.15,0:36:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,electively by his intention,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.22,0:36:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,sets what the energy field is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.22,0:36:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But then the energy field itself
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.22,0:36:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes impersonal.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.22,0:36:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens is you see a sudden
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.22,0:36:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,severe reversal of the energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.22,0:36:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And now when you come back a year later,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.22,0:36:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,a year later,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.22,0:36:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and you look at the barn,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.22,0:36:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,or let's say you take aerial photographs,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.22,0:36:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and you come back a year later,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.22,0:36:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you will see from the aerial photograph
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.22,0:36:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that the foliage in that canyon has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.31,0:36:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,When you visit the barn,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.31,0:36:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you will see that there are now holes in the roof,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.31,0:36:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and there are now packrats living there,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.31,0:36:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and there are cockroaches there,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.31,0:36:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and all that is negative
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.31,0:36:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,seems to be pulled into this barn,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.31,0:36:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and a quarter of it has fallen down,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.31,0:36:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and teenagers have kicked the slats out
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.31,0:36:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and broken the windows,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.31,0:36:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and you wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.31,0:37:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I saw it happen to a little cottage
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.31,0:37:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,across the creek from where I live,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.31,0:37:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,in a beautiful, happy little thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.31,0:37:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,through abandonment,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.31,0:37:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and for one thing or another,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.31,0:37:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,its energy got reversed,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.31,0:37:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and now teenagers were like pulled,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.31,0:37:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, like rats and things,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.31,0:37:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and they kicked all the sides in,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.31,0:37:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and they kicked the roof in,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.31,0:37:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and they kicked the walls in,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.31,0:37:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and they kicked the windows out,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.31,0:37:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and they kicked the doors in,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.31,0:37:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and each time I would visit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.31,0:37:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,some more things had been kicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.31,0:37:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So once the thing reverses, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.31,0:37:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it pulls further destruction to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.31,0:37:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.56,0:37:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason to say that is to get the feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.56,0:37:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,of impersonality.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.56,0:37:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the energy field now
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.56,0:37:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,which pulls that destructive.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.56,0:37:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So the antenna then,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.56,0:37:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's tuned to negative,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.56,0:37:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's tuned to reverse,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.56,0:37:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,then pulls into the person's life
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.56,0:37:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,all that is destructive,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.56,0:37:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,so that the person below this level then
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.56,0:37:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is experiencing that reversity,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.72,0:37:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that negativity in the form
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.72,0:38:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,of all kinds of adversity.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.72,0:38:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So it can be a DWI,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.72,0:38:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it can be parking ticket starts out mild,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.72,0:38:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,parking tickets,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.72,0:38:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it gets a little worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.72,0:38:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,DWIs, and then bankruptcies,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.72,0:38:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and you lost your credit rating,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.72,0:38:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and the next thing you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.72,0:38:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you find yourself in the county jail,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.72,0:38:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and your relationships go to hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.72,0:38:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and your family disappears,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.72,0:38:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and the indebtedness,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.39,0:38:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.39,0:38:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,they take away your credit card.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.39,0:38:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So the destruction and the destitution,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.39,0:38:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course the inner destruction is going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.39,0:38:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's what eventually brings people
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.39,0:38:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,into seeking help.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.58,0:38:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field of courage then is crucial
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.58,0:38:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,because the antenna,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.58,0:38:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,which was too negative, destructive,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.58,0:38:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and pulling into the person's life
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.58,0:38:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,all that is destructive in the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.58,0:38:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,now goes neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.58,0:38:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So that process now,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.58,0:38:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say the person is equally constructive
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.58,0:38:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and destructive,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.58,0:38:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,so that it neutralizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.58,0:38:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The antenna now goes neutral,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.58,0:38:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and the energy field is no longer reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.58,0:38:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,200 is a lot of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.58,0:39:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It gives the person the capacity to face,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.58,0:39:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to cope,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.58,0:39:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to go into appropriate action.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.61,0:39:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And the process going on in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.74,0:39:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of empowerment.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.74,0:39:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And how does that come about?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.22,0:39:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes about as a result,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.47,0:39:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,how does the energy field reverse itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.47,0:39:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes about as a result of telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.47,0:39:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So that, which is below the line,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.47,0:39:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.47,0:39:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is the selling out of the truth about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.86,0:39:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The selling out of the truth reverses the energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.86,0:39:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and brings to the person destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.86,0:39:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The way out, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.86,0:39:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is by stating the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.17,0:39:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The difficulty is a person down at this level
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.17,0:39:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,looks within himself and says,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.17,0:39:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,if I looked at the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.17,0:39:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.17,0:39:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And you will hear people in the 12-step groups
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.17,0:39:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,who will tell you they've been in the program for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.17,0:39:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They've taken the first step,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.17,0:39:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe the second step,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.17,0:39:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the third step,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.46,0:39:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,they even do 12-step work.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.46,0:40:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But the fourth step,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.46,0:40:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,which is one of a personal fearless moral inventory,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.46,0:40:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,many of them can't handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.46,0:40:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason is because the person looks at all this
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.87,0:40:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and they say,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.87,0:40:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,this person here,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.87,0:40:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,this person here,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.87,0:40:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,a reversed 100 person that I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.87,0:40:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot handle what's going to come up
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.97,0:40:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,if I start telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.42,0:40:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, what they don't know is that the minute you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.61,0:40:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you see you're walking off a cliff,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.61,0:40:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't know it,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.61,0:40:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but when you do walk off the cliff and tell the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.61,0:40:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens is you pull yourself from the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.61,0:40:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the power to face what comes up
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.61,0:40:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,as a result of telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.61,0:40:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't get the power until you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.67,0:40:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the first step then in the 12-step programs.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.67,0:40:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Admit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.67,0:40:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,we are powerless over some addictive substance
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.67,0:40:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,or people do it in their daily life
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.67,0:40:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,who are not into the addictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.67,0:40:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute you admit the truth about something,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.67,0:40:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,then this reversity stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.67,0:41:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field goes neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.67,0:41:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You pull to yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.67,0:41:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy field is 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.67,0:41:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,which has,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.67,0:41:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacity to face, to cope,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.67,0:41:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and to handle it with appropriate action.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.67,0:41:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What has the power?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.67,0:41:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field has the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.67,0:41:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field is what has the power to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.67,0:41:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So you summon to yourself an energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.67,0:41:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that has the power to handle it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.67,0:41:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And as your own consciousness gets higher,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.67,0:41:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you realize that it is being done like through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.67,0:41:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not your personal self.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.67,0:41:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Your personal self has summoned it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.67,0:41:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,through its own free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.67,0:41:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It has summoned it forth,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.67,0:41:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but now it is the field that is handling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.96,0:41:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You move up to the next higher level then,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.96,0:41:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the courage to face, to cope,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.96,0:41:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to take appropriate action in the addictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.96,0:41:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In the addictions and to let go the resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.96,0:41:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,To let go the resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.96,0:41:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And through that empowerment now,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.12,0:41:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to let go resisting
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.12,0:41:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and move up through an energy field which,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.12,0:41:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,we calibrate out at about 250.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.44,0:42:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's often accompanied by a feeling of detachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.44,0:42:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That this is, it's all okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.44,0:42:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay if this happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.44,0:42:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay if it doesn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.57,0:42:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And the process going on in consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.16,0:42:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we say is the person has become released.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.16,0:42:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They've become released in that they've let go,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.16,0:42:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.16,0:42:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They have let go the resistance to however it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.16,0:42:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So they say,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.19,0:42:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,if I get a new car, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.26,0:42:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I don't get a new car, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.42,0:42:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This company wants to keep me, swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.42,0:42:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And if they want to let me go,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.42,0:42:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find another job.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.42,0:42:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's a great field to be in
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.42,0:42:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,if you've been down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.42,0:42:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To be up in neutral at least,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.42,0:42:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have the painful experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.42,0:42:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, in courage, you have the energy
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.42,0:42:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to handle these lower feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.42,0:42:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but they haven't disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.93,0:42:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The person in courage goes to ask the boss for a raise.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.93,0:42:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,His stomach is in a knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.93,0:42:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,See, his stomach can be in a knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.93,0:43:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He can be run by this desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.93,0:43:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He can be angry that he's got to go and ask in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.93,0:43:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He can be resentful and have all kinds of self-pity down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.93,0:43:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This value to the company wasn't recognized
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.93,0:43:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and he had to go and ask for it, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.93,0:43:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So he has all these negative feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.54,0:43:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But the courage, the power of courage at 200
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.54,0:43:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,has the power to handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.57,0:43:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And so he acts appropriately
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.57,0:43:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,despite the negative feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.57,0:43:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As you move up into neutral,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.57,0:43:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,where you become no longer attached to outcome,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.57,0:43:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,then you energize,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.57,0:43:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you get a feeling of being released about the matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.57,0:43:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and these feelings begin to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.57,0:43:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,These feelings disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.57,0:43:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're totally released on it, it's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.57,0:43:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The boss gives you the raise, fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.57,0:43:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And if he doesn't, you live with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.57,0:43:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a great field to be in
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.57,0:43:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,as compared to having your stomach in a knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.57,0:43:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the person at the bottom wouldn't even ask for a raise
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.57,0:43:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,because, in his view, he would be worthless
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.57,0:43:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and the boss would never give him a raise anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.57,0:43:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to move up higher
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.82,0:44:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to even take appropriate action.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.82,0:44:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So this allows the person
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.82,0:44:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to become easygoing
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.08,0:44:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and move up into the next energy field called acceptance.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.08,0:44:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Acceptance is a much higher field.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.08,0:44:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates out at 380.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.08,0:44:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,At that level, the person is easygoing
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.72,0:44:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and confident and capable.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.72,0:44:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And we see that there's the beginning now
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.72,0:44:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,of a transformation in consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.72,0:44:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,a growing awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.72,0:44:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is the growing awareness from?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.72,0:44:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The growing awareness is coming from
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.72,0:44:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the realization
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.72,0:44:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that the power,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.72,0:44:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the power to be happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.72,0:44:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the source of happiness in my life is within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.72,0:44:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one that decides
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.75,0:44:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,whether I'm going to be successful or happy
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.75,0:44:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,in any situation or relationship or position.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.65,0:44:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Below the level of courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.65,0:44:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody, because they're victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.65,0:44:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,thinks that it is out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.65,0:45:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The power is out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.90,0:45:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Cadillac that will do it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.90,0:45:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the position, it's the title, it's the address,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.90,0:45:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the suit of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.90,0:45:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something out there will do it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.90,0:45:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the relationship,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.90,0:45:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the her in my life or the him in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.86,0:45:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the PhD degree or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.86,0:45:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what's going to do it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.86,0:45:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But as you move up to this higher energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.86,0:45:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,there's the realization
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.86,0:45:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that the power to create happiness and success in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.86,0:45:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,lies within me and me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.86,0:45:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's arising out of my positions,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.86,0:45:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it's arising out of my decisions,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.86,0:45:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it's arising out of my intentions,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.86,0:45:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,my goals, my purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.86,0:45:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's arising out of that which I value.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.86,0:45:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And what I value is arising out of the meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.86,0:45:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's arising out of the context.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.86,0:45:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beginning to arise out of that which I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.86,0:45:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So that transformation of that awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.86,0:45:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,then gives the person a great deal more power.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.86,0:45:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They're no longer dependent on the world as the source.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.86,0:45:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,See, down here the world has to amuse you
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.28,0:46:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's nothing more panicky than your TV set going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.28,0:46:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Or being all alone by yourself with nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.70,0:46:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.70,0:46:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to sit in a bus station for three hours
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.70,0:46:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,with nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.86,0:46:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And the magazine stand is closed
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.86,0:46:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's no TV and there's no radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.86,0:46:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And there you are all by yourself in a bus station
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.86,0:46:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle of nowhere
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.86,0:46:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and you've got four hours to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.86,0:46:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This would be death to these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.92,0:46:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there's nothing out there to hang on to.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.92,0:46:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no beauty out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.92,0:46:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no aesthetic amusement.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.92,0:46:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no action.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.34,0:46:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Here a person would say,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.34,0:46:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,fantastic, wow, I've got three and a half hours
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.34,0:46:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've got so much stuff to work on myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.34,0:46:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what a lucky break.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.34,0:46:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.34,0:46:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can barely catch up in four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.34,0:46:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All the stuff I've got to handle in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.34,0:46:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They would think it's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.46,0:46:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So that power then,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.46,0:46:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that person in that energy state knows
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.46,0:46:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,if you drop them in a desert island someplace
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.46,0:46:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle of the Atlantic or Pacific Ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.46,0:46:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you come back a year later
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.46,0:46:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll have a coconut factory going.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.46,0:47:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be teaching the natives French.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.46,0:47:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have found a cute little native girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.46,0:47:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll build a tree house.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.46,0:47:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That capacity to create for yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.46,0:47:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,out of what is around you,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.46,0:47:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to make a garden there,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.46,0:47:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to grow things there,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.46,0:47:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to create an industry,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.46,0:47:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to create something where the energy flows back to you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.46,0:47:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,with the happiness of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.46,0:47:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So we all know that level in ourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.46,0:47:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What the world calls important
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.46,0:47:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't really mean anything
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.46,0:47:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,when you just found the missing nut
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.46,0:47:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that allowed you to fix the fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.46,0:47:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you know how happy that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.46,0:47:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you just found your crochet hook
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.46,0:47:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can't finish the thing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.46,0:47:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the little things that make your whole day delightful.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.46,0:47:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And how many times in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.46,0:47:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,has it become a delight over some little thing, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.46,0:47:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I just finished a chicken coop
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.46,0:47:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and the chickens are happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.46,0:47:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what could make you happier, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.46,0:47:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What the world thinks and all the tiles on it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.46,0:47:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean anything
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.46,0:47:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,because what you're experiencing is joy
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.46,0:47:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,with the right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.46,0:47:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,with the right now of what it all is to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.46,0:47:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The joy of your own existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.46,0:48:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To experience the joy of your own existence
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.46,0:48:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,then moves you up
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.46,0:48:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're moving up to the next energy level.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.46,0:48:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we call love.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.53,0:48:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is, in this context then,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.53,0:48:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at an energy field of 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.53,0:48:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the beginning of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.53,0:48:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness, if you calibrate it, comes out at 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.53,0:48:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A very crucial level,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.53,0:48:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,a very crucial level
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.53,0:48:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,for us to work in the addictions
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.53,0:48:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,because we're moving into the energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.53,0:48:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of the self-help groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.53,0:48:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Alcoholics Anonymous calibrates out at 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.53,0:48:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy fields of love
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.10,0:48:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and these are not the sentimental emotionalism of love
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.10,0:48:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that the world talks about
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.10,0:48:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but a powerful, stable, unconditional energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.52,0:48:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that you set by your own intention,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.52,0:48:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,by your own decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.52,0:48:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,by that to which you say yes in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.32,0:48:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy field of 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.32,0:49:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,As you move into the energy fields of 500 and up,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.32,0:49:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,about 540,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.32,0:49:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Alcoholics Anonymous really calibrates at 540
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.32,0:49:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the energy field of healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.32,0:49:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When you calibrate the energy field of healing,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.32,0:49:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it is around 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.32,0:49:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That means that the energy field alone of the group,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.32,0:49:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,irrespective of what they talk about,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.32,0:49:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,irrespective of the whole program,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.32,0:49:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the wording, the phrasing, the languaging of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.32,0:49:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy field of that
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.38,0:49:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is in itself healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.38,0:49:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore you hear statements
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.38,0:49:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in which this is intuited.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.38,0:49:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They will say,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.38,0:49:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,just bring the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.38,0:49:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,just bring the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.38,0:49:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that people get just as sober
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.38,0:49:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,if they're ordered there by the court
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.38,0:49:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,as if they go there voluntarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.38,0:49:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And somebody I know
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.38,0:49:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,quite well in one of the groups
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.77,0:49:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,was just ordered there to the court
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.77,0:49:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,because he had three DWIs
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.77,0:49:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and he had a choice between a year in jail
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.77,0:49:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,or going to AA.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.77,0:49:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end of a year,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.77,0:49:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,when his sentence was up,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.77,0:49:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,he wouldn't have left it for the world
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.77,0:49:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,because his own consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.77,0:50:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,had become transformed.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.38,0:50:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is sort of like,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.38,0:50:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you might say,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.38,0:50:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,an electromagnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.38,0:50:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a field phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.38,0:50:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,An energy field of 540
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.38,0:50:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,heals anything you put in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.38,0:50:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sick rabbits,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.38,0:50:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,wounded legs,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.38,0:50:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,people in despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.38,0:50:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,people addicted to substances,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.38,0:50:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.38,0:50:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you picture it like an impersonal
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.38,0:50:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,electromagnetic energy field then,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.38,0:50:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,with a certain power,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.38,0:50:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a power that we calibrate,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.38,0:50:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say you set the dial at 540,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.38,0:50:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,then whatever you set in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.38,0:50:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,set in it is going to begin to heal
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.38,0:50:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.38,0:50:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of love we're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.38,0:50:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,never dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.38,0:50:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't a such thing
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.38,0:50:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,as unconditional love dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.38,0:50:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.44,0:50:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it is a decision
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.44,0:50:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that you make within yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.44,0:50:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that sets up an energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.44,0:50:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,which is stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.44,0:50:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So that which is unconditional love
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.44,0:50:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is unchanging.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.44,0:50:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Unchanging.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.60,0:50:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Within the energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.60,0:50:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,of unconditional love
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.60,0:50:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to which you've committed yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.60,0:51:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the negative emotions may come and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.63,0:51:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You may hate the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.63,0:51:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.63,0:51:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.63,0:51:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a passing emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.63,0:51:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And the person's unconditional love
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.63,0:51:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,has not changed their commitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.63,0:51:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It has not changed their commitment at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.63,0:51:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a passing emotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.63,0:51:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is only passing within
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.63,0:51:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,a greater energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.63,0:51:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course they know
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.63,0:51:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,they're going to forgive the other person.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.63,0:51:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course they know
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.63,0:51:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that they're going to make up.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.63,0:51:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course they know
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.63,0:51:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,they're not going to hang on
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.63,0:51:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to this resentment any longer
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.63,0:51:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,than it takes to get rid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.63,0:51:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So the person in this level then
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.63,0:51:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,is characterized in their emotional state
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.63,0:51:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,by a caring for,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.63,0:51:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,a nurturing,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.63,0:51:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,a support,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.63,0:51:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,a willingness to forgive,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.63,0:51:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,a willingness to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.08,0:51:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is the question then
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.08,0:51:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,in the person's mind
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.08,0:51:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,in this energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.08,0:51:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is to understand that,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.08,0:51:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.21,0:51:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,See, down here the idea is to make it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.21,0:51:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's right and who's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.21,0:51:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Here the intention is right and wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.21,0:52:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Here the intention is not even interested
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.21,0:52:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,in right and wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.21,0:52:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's totally irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.21,0:52:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get into an argument,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.24,0:52:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,if people in this level
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.24,0:52:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,get into an argument,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.24,0:52:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,nobody even cares
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.24,0:52:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.24,0:52:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What they want to know
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.24,0:52:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is what's out with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.24,0:52:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What don't we understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.24,0:52:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, where is it coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.24,0:52:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it karma?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.24,0:52:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.24,0:52:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a past life?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.24,0:52:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it something going on
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.24,0:52:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm not aware of?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.24,0:52:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that's not healed in me
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.24,0:52:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that's bringing it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.24,0:52:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there's the beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.24,0:52:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,of a revelation, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.24,0:52:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The beginning of transformation now
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.24,0:52:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is bringing you
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.24,0:52:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to certain inner revelations.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.24,0:52:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And you begin to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.24,0:52:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that when things
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.24,0:52:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,are not going smoothly,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.24,0:52:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's merely something
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.24,0:52:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to be handled.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.24,0:52:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something that's
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.24,0:52:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,not understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.24,0:52:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And then when it's
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.24,0:52:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,correctly understood,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.24,0:52:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,because it is now held
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.24,0:52:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,from the viewpoint
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.24,0:52:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,of understanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.24,0:52:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the understanding itself
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.24,0:52:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,heals that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.24,0:52:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So that you can't
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.24,0:52:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,stay mad at a person
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.24,0:52:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in the field
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.24,0:52:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,of unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.24,0:52:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.24,0:52:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,we're all aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.24,0:52:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one of the whole intentions
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.24,0:52:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,of the consciousness movement
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.56,0:53:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and all that is called
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.56,0:53:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,New Age and etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.56,0:53:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,As we know,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.69,0:53:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that a resentment
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.69,0:53:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is your problem
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.69,0:53:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to handle and get off,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.69,0:53:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.69,0:53:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To get off the resentment
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.69,0:53:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.69,0:53:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not up
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.69,0:53:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to the other problem
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.69,0:53:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.69,0:53:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you don't like the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.07,0:53:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that he wears a vest
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.07,0:53:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.07,0:53:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that's your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.07,0:53:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the other fellow's
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.07,0:53:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,problem to no longer
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.07,0:53:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,wear a vest.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.07,0:53:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.07,0:53:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why that bothers you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.07,0:53:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So that brings us
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.07,0:53:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,then into a powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.07,0:53:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.07,0:53:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,which is coming out
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.07,0:53:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of our intention
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.07,0:53:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to be that kind of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.07,0:53:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So we might say
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.07,0:53:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that we could call
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.07,0:53:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,this level here
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.07,0:53:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.07,0:53:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.07,0:53:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We say that a person
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.07,0:53:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.07,0:53:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,what they're showing
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.26,0:53:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.26,0:53:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This quality goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.26,0:53:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,with them all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.26,0:53:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So their relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.39,0:53:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to things
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.39,0:53:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.39,0:53:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,To nurture that beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.39,0:53:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.74,0:53:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Their relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.74,0:53:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to animals
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.74,0:53:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.74,0:53:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Their relationships
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.74,0:53:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to all things
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.74,0:53:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.74,0:54:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A lovingness towards life
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.74,0:54:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and a lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.74,0:54:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,towards life.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.74,0:54:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Towards beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.74,0:54:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and the desire
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.74,0:54:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to support that
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.74,0:54:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.13,0:54:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So relationships
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.13,0:54:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,coming out of that
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.13,0:54:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,are then unconditional.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.13,0:54:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning non-judgmental.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.13,0:54:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no interest
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.13,0:54:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,in rightness
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.13,0:54:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and wrongness.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.13,0:54:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So characteristic
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.13,0:54:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of the 12-step group.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.13,0:54:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's say
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.13,0:54:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody who's been in AA
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.13,0:54:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,would have a slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.13,0:54:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And while they're
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.13,0:54:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,on the slip
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.13,0:54:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,they shot three people
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.13,0:54:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and ran over four infants
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.13,0:54:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and destroyed a building.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.13,0:54:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,When they come back
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.13,0:54:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to the group
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.13,0:54:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,what does everybody say?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.13,0:54:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,George.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.13,0:54:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.13,0:54:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to have you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.13,0:54:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.13,0:54:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.13,0:54:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to have you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.13,0:54:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no interest
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.13,0:54:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,in a moralistic condemnation.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.13,0:54:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.13,0:54:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,an interest
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.13,0:54:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,in what the person is.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.13,0:54:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's because
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.13,0:54:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,they're relating
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.13,0:54:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,they're beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.13,0:54:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to relate now
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.13,0:54:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to the person's beingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.13,0:54:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That which they really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.58,0:54:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So the mother
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.58,0:54:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,who visits her son
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.58,0:54:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,in prison
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.58,0:54:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,for 20 years
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.58,0:54:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,a murderer
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.58,0:54:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,in prison
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.58,0:54:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and when I was
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.58,0:55:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,a doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.58,0:55:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,in the state hospitals
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.58,0:55:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,we had situations
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.58,0:55:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.58,0:55:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,People
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.58,0:55:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,extremely psychotic
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.58,0:55:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and in their
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.58,0:55:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,psychotic behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.58,0:55:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,they had done
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.58,0:55:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,really terrible things
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.58,0:55:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,almost a terrible
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.58,0:55:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.58,0:55:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet the mothers
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.58,0:55:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the families
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.58,0:55:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,would come
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.58,0:55:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and visit them
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.58,0:55:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.58,0:55:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.58,0:55:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So the unconditional love
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.58,0:55:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,then
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.58,0:55:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,overlooks
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.58,0:55:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,what the behavior is.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.58,0:55:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It says
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.58,0:55:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.58,0:55:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.58,0:55:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming out
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.58,0:55:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of that
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.58,0:55:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,which is not understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.58,0:55:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming out
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.58,0:55:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of illness
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.58,0:55:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,it's coming out
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.58,0:55:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of unknowingness
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.58,0:55:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,it's coming out
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.58,0:55:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of ignorance
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.58,0:55:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is not really
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.58,0:55:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,something greater than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.58,0:55:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And so
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.58,0:55:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,in Outlawics Anonymous
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.58,0:55:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,then what the people
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.58,0:55:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,relate to
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.58,0:55:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is that which you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.58,0:55:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And the behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.58,0:55:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is overlooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.58,0:55:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody cares
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.58,0:55:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,what you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.58,0:55:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,See at the bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.67,0:55:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,of the box
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.67,0:55:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,people are interested
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.67,0:55:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,in what you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.67,0:55:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.67,0:55:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Possessions
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.67,0:55:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and titles
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.67,0:55:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and appearances
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.67,0:55:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and things
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.67,0:55:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,all having to do
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.67,0:55:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,with have.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.67,0:55:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle of the box
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.67,0:55:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,people are interested
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.67,0:56:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,in what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.67,0:56:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,See your titles
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.67,0:56:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,what you do
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.67,0:56:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.67,0:56:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.67,0:56:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But as you move towards
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.67,0:56:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the top of the box
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.67,0:56:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,what people are interested in
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.67,0:56:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.67,0:56:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.67,0:56:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And so
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.67,0:56:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.67,0:56:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,in recovery
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.67,0:56:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,from addictions
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.47,0:56:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,in AA
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.47,0:56:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,for instance
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.46,0:56:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,nobody cares
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.46,0:56:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,about what you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.46,0:56:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can know somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.46,0:56:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,for 20 years
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.46,0:56:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and have them
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.46,0:56:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,disliked
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.46,0:56:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,about what they have
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.46,0:56:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,or interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.46,0:56:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You may even
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.62,0:56:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,after 20 years
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.62,0:56:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,still not really
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.62,0:56:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,even know
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.62,0:56:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,what they do
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.62,0:56:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,despite the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.62,0:56:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that you've talked
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.62,0:56:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to them
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.62,0:56:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,on the most intimate level
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.62,0:56:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,about the most mind-boggling
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.62,0:56:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,thing anybody else
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.62,0:56:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world about.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.62,0:56:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You still at this point
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.88,0:56:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,don't even know
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.88,0:56:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,what the person does.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.88,0:56:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.88,0:56:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you do again?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.88,0:56:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget what it is
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.88,0:56:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,an engineer or something
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.88,0:56:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.88,0:56:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What the person is
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.88,0:56:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that is what
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.88,0:56:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is all important.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.88,0:56:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.88,0:56:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of what they are
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.88,0:56:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that you honor them
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.88,0:56:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and you protect them
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.42,0:56:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and you support that
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.42,0:56:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and you forgive them
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.42,0:56:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and when they forget
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.42,0:56:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.42,0:56:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which they are
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.42,0:57:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,then you hold that
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.42,0:57:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,for them
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.42,0:57:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and remind them
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.42,0:57:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,of that.
