Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.88,1:11:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,tell the former
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.88,1:11:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,person who's
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.88,1:11:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,experienced this
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.88,1:11:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you should really
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.88,1:11:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,get a new job
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.88,1:11:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and get a hobby
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.88,1:11:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and move to Cincinnati
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.88,1:11:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and quit that girlfriend
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.88,1:11:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and move out
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.88,1:11:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of your mother's house
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.88,1:11:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,alright
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.88,1:11:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,what we're suggesting
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.88,1:11:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is a 200
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.88,1:11:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,solution
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.88,1:11:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to a 600
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.88,1:11:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,experience
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.88,1:11:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's why
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.88,1:11:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't work
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.33,1:11:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,a 600
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.33,1:11:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,energy problem
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.33,1:11:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,requires
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.33,1:11:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,a 600
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.06,1:11:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,energy answer
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.06,1:11:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and so
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.06,1:11:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,in Shangri-La
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.06,1:11:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you see
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.06,1:11:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,finally
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.06,1:11:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,he tries his best
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.06,1:11:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to do what he can
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.06,1:11:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,within the world
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.06,1:11:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but the memory
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.06,1:11:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,of that
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.06,1:11:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the knowing
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.06,1:11:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,of that
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.06,1:11:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,inner experience
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.06,1:11:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,because in Shangri-La
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.06,1:11:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,what you experience
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.06,1:11:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.06,1:12:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,of your own
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.06,1:12:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,isness
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.90,1:12:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and so
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.90,1:12:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,he lets go
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.90,1:12:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of everything
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.90,1:12:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.90,1:12:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and he struggles
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.90,1:12:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to go back
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.90,1:12:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,into Shangri-La
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.90,1:12:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and in so
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.90,1:12:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,doing
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.90,1:12:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,he sacrifices
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.90,1:12:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,everything
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.90,1:12:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,sacrifices
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.90,1:12:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,everything
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.90,1:12:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and becomes
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.90,1:12:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,like a madman
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.90,1:12:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,they say
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.90,1:12:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,he's like a madman
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.90,1:12:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,as he went
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.90,1:12:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,through the villages
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.90,1:12:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and finally
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.90,1:12:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,even the Sherpas
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.90,1:12:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,desert him
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.90,1:12:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's left
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.90,1:12:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,all by himself
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.90,1:12:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the lone survivor
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.90,1:12:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,who finally
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.90,1:12:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,at the point of death
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.90,1:12:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,gets back
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.90,1:12:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to Shangri-La
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.90,1:12:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.90,1:12:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,a very
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.90,1:12:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,difficult time
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.90,1:12:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it's different
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.90,1:12:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,this time
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.90,1:12:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the struggle
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.90,1:12:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,see
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.90,1:12:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the first time
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.90,1:12:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,he lands there
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.90,1:12:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,by accident
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.90,1:12:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,karmically
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.90,1:12:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you might say
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.93,1:12:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the plane lands
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.93,1:12:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,within striking distance
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.93,1:12:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and he
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.93,1:12:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,gets there
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.93,1:12:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but the second time
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.93,1:12:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,it is only
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.22,1:12:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.22,1:12:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,through his own
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.34,1:12:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,personal effort
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.34,1:12:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and constant
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.34,1:12:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,recommitment
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.34,1:12:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,he has to say
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.34,1:12:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.34,1:12:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,every step of the way
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.34,1:12:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,when he landed
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.34,1:12:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,there by accident
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.34,1:13:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,he didn't have to
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.34,1:13:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and say yes to it. He has to say yes to every step of the way to get back to that mountain pass.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.90,1:13:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And then he returns to Shangri-La, but this time it is different. He is now himself the one who
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.04,1:13:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,holds that for Shangri-La. You remember the old leader of the community had died in the interim,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.87,1:13:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and now he was the one holding that level of consciousness for the group. So the power then
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.54,1:13:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of that experience, the power of that experience. So what happens of course with the drugs is the
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.50,1:13:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,drugs don't have any power to create a state of highness. Drugs have no power at all. We will
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.60,1:13:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,test this out in the class today and prove it. It's a critical point. It's why the world can't
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.98,1:13:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,handle the drug experience. It doesn't know what it is. What the person then is addicted to is the
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.77,1:13:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,re-experiencing of this energy field.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.15,1:14:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Drugs block off the shadows, they block off the
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.42,1:14:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,clouds and allow you to experience a vibration
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.24,1:14:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and energy field which is always there. But the drug itself does not have the power to create
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.94,1:14:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that experience. It only has the power to remove the block to that experience,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.10,1:14:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that experience which would be there all the time for everyone, all the time,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.00,1:14:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,if it weren't for what's-in-the-box blocking our awareness of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.66,1:14:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So all the drugs
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.06,1:14:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,does is clear the field for you to experience something that is already
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.36,1:14:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,there. It has no power to create that whatsoever. Drug has no power to create
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.70,1:14:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,any high at all. It only has the power to block off that which is not the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.52,1:14:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,about yourself and get closer to the energy and the feeling and the inner
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.30,1:14:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,vibration of that which is. That's why it is so addicting, see, because then the
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.51,1:14:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,left brain says, the left brain gets that sequence. It gets to take the drug, move
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.55,1:15:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,up in the box, experience that feeling. It must be in the box. It must be in the
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.37,1:15:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,drug. It must be in the drug. An aew person thinks it must be in the drug.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.01,1:15:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,People, who in the great days of LSD, took LSD with proper preparation, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.19,1:15:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Spent a year of meditation and fasting and spiritual study, took it once, walked
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.26,1:15:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,out of that which they were and experienced that which was there since
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.82,1:15:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the beginning of time. They walked into that which always was.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.28,1:15:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,. . .
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.38,1:15:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and realized the truth of that, what that was, and never took it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.56,1:15:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,People who really took LSD correctly took it maybe once, maximum twice.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.10,1:15:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it was very obvious that it wasn't a drug at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.76,1:15:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All the drug had done was remove your ability to witness that which is.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.46,1:15:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And the realization of that which is then,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.18,1:15:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, the people came out of that with an intense spiritual commitment,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.04,1:15:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and you saw a great rise in spiritual commitment to spiritual values and all,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.62,1:16:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and then people spent the rest of their lives purifying themselves
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.36,1:16:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to return to a state which only through the LSD experience,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.60,1:16:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say for them perhaps, did they verify the truth of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.70,1:16:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So the person suspected this is so, verified this is so,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.82,1:16:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and now spends the rest of their life returning to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.28,1:16:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody with any awareness realizes, obviously,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.34,1:16:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that you cannot experience the truth of that which you are by repeatedly taking LSD.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.14,1:16:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that was sort of retarded.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.06,1:16:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the right way to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.19,1:16:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody who really took it in the proper context took it once.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.32,1:16:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because all it did was verify for you that that is always there,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.32,1:16:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that it is what it is,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.32,1:16:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and that you see that which is within you is blocking your awareness of that experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.32,1:16:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The work of removing that which is blocking the experience then
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.32,1:16:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is what the rest of your life is dedicated to.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.32,1:16:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So that would be how to do it consciously.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.32,1:16:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people say,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.51,1:17:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,well, of course, did not do it consciously,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.51,1:17:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and instead for the glamour and the sensation of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.51,1:17:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But people who had a transcendental experience,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.51,1:17:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,which happened in the very early days,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.51,1:17:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,because it was then, in those days, considered a sacrament,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.51,1:17:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it allowed you, as Aldous Huxley said,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.51,1:17:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it opened the doors of perception,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.51,1:17:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,allowed you to experience that which is.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.51,1:17:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But the drug does not create that which is.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.51,1:17:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, that is one of the great problems in the drug experience,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.51,1:17:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the left brain begins to think that it is,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.51,1:17:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,for the person who has never had that experience otherwise,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.80,1:17:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that the power is in the drug.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.80,1:17:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The power is in the drug.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.80,1:17:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The person thinks the power is in the drug.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.80,1:17:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, in the beginning, a person, let's say, is nervous,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.25,1:17:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and self-conscious, and etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.25,1:17:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And they stop by, and they have two martinis,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.25,1:17:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and now they go into a mellow,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.25,1:17:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and they go to this business conference,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.25,1:17:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and they carry it out successfully.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.25,1:17:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, nobody is being harmed, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.25,1:18:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no scandal being created.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.25,1:18:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.25,1:18:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with moving from a negative energy field,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.25,1:18:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,resentment, let's say, and nervousness, and anxiety,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.25,1:18:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and moving into a lovingness,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.25,1:18:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,where you are concerned about the welfare of humanity,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.25,1:18:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and love, and generosity?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.92,1:18:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.92,1:18:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it end up in such a disaster?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.92,1:18:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, how come it ends up in the pits of hell?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.92,1:18:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How does the energy field get reversed?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.53,1:18:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, why does it go from a positive,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.53,1:18:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,mellow, happy lovingness,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.53,1:18:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to a hatefulness?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.53,1:18:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The father that used to have a drink or two on his way home,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.53,1:18:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and come home happy, and the kids love to see him,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.53,1:18:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,now as the years go by, comes home nasty,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.53,1:18:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and selfish, and then becomes physically violent,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.53,1:18:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and everybody hates him, and fears him,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.53,1:18:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and finally the family breaks up.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.53,1:18:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.53,1:18:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's only doing the same thing he did in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.53,1:18:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In the beginning he stopped for two martinis,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.72,1:18:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and he came home mellow.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.72,1:18:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he stops for two martinis,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.72,1:18:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and he comes home violent and nasty.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.72,1:18:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What has changed?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.75,1:19:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What has happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.75,1:19:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What has been the critical?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.75,1:19:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.14,1:19:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on is that he's given the power to the drugs,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.14,1:19:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,in my own particular research into the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.49,1:19:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happened is that the energy field,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.49,1:19:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,we said that the truth puts you above the line.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.49,1:19:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If truth puts you above the line,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.65,1:19:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,then a lie puts you below the line.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.65,1:19:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So when he gives the power to the drug,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.65,1:19:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,when he gives the power to the drug,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.84,1:19:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,then what happens is he reverses the energy field,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.84,1:19:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,because the lie, the telling of the untruth,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.84,1:19:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is what reverses the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.38,1:19:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now a lie that's told at a minus 50,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.38,1:19:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say you're down in apathy at 50,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.38,1:19:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,your life is one entire lie anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.38,1:19:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole context of your life is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.38,1:19:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And all you do is lie all day long anyway,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.38,1:19:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,so one more lie doesn't really have that profound an effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.38,1:19:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you're in a very high state,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.63,1:19:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and you owe the lie,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.21,1:19:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the effect is disastrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.21,1:20:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A lie with a power of 550 behind it
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.21,1:20:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is quite a different lie
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.21,1:20:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,than a thought with an energy field of 50 behind it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.50,1:20:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A lie at 550 has,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.50,1:20:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,can totally reverse all your energies
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.50,1:20:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and totally transform your life now into destruction.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.50,1:20:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So we see,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.50,1:20:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the giving of the power,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.50,1:20:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the power, the truth of that which you are,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.50,1:20:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you now deny,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.50,1:20:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and you say it does not exist within me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.50,1:20:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,On the contrary, it exists out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.50,1:20:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It is within that.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.50,1:20:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And the giving away the truth of that which you are
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.50,1:20:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,then reverses the energy field.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.50,1:20:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you want, later we can test that out,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.88,1:20:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,test out the truth of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.10,1:20:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is the ascribing of the power,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.10,1:20:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth of that which you are,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.10,1:20:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to something that is outside of you that you are not.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.10,1:20:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is that statement
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.10,1:20:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,which is made in a high energy state.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.10,1:20:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,See, it is in the high energy state that you say,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.10,1:20:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,it is that that created this.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.10,1:20:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't say that in a low energy state,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.26,1:20:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you said that in a high energy state.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.26,1:21:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,With a lot of power.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.26,1:21:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,550 is a lot of power.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.46,1:21:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So in a high energy state you said,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.46,1:21:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the power is in that.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.46,1:21:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It is that that I worship.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.46,1:21:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I worship. It has become my idol.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.46,1:21:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the center of my life now.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.46,1:21:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,God has been really replaced by that.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.46,1:21:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That which I am has been replaced by that.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.46,1:21:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The giving of the power away then to that
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.62,1:21:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,is what reverses the energy field.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.62,1:21:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So now, that which at one time you got high,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.13,1:21:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,now sends you into destruction.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.13,1:21:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The very same thing now is the two-faced genus.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.13,1:21:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly its face turns around
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.13,1:21:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see that the energy field has reversed.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.13,1:21:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That which once was positive in your life
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.13,1:21:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is now the most destructive thing in your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.13,1:21:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought, well, we'll take a break now
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.80,1:21:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that we've gotten to what the addiction is.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.80,1:21:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The addiction is to that state of consciousness called bliss.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.80,1:21:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It really has nothing at all to do with the drug.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.80,1:21:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And the drug comes in accidentally in our society,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.80,1:22:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because most people don't meditate themselves
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.80,1:22:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in the states of samadhi.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.80,1:22:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They experience that state only through drugs.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.80,1:22:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore it is a phenomenon of our society
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.80,1:22:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of being a materialistic culture.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.80,1:22:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I said this afternoon we'll test out,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.93,1:22:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll use, for instance, kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.93,1:22:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,to test out the truth of some of the statements we've made.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.93,1:22:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially, and most importantly,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.93,1:22:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the one that people who themselves have become addicted
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.93,1:22:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,are most impressed by,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.93,1:22:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is the awareness of what it is they're addicted to.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.82,1:22:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,After saying this for some time, a year or two,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.82,1:22:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran across a writing by Ramana Maharshi.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.82,1:22:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramana Maharshi being one of the great saints of India,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.82,1:22:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightened in the view of the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.02,1:22:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and a very famous person.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.17,1:22:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway, Ramana Maharshi said,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.17,1:22:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,in one of his books that I ran across,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.17,1:23:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that the reason the person becomes intoxicated
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.84,1:23:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is to experience the self.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.90,1:23:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And that once a person learns what it is they are seeking
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.19,1:23:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,through the intoxication,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.19,1:23:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,they will then seek that directly.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.19,1:23:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought it was very interesting,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.19,1:23:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,because Ramana Maharshi never took a drink in his life.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.19,1:23:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He knew nothing about addiction,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.80,1:23:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet he knew that.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.80,1:23:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That once the person realizes what it is they are seeking,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.18,1:23:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that inner experience in consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.18,1:23:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,once they realize what that is,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.18,1:23:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,they will then begin to seek it directly.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.18,1:23:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, that's the whole function of 12-step groups.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.11,1:23:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the whole function of Alcoholics Anonymous.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.11,1:23:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So now we can see,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.11,1:23:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,from a viewpoint of consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.14,1:23:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,we have some greater understanding then,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.24,1:23:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,of how the 12 steps work,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.24,1:24:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and how the whole field, the energy field, of AA works.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.24,1:24:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we see in the first step,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.24,1:24:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the first step was we admitted we were powerless.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.24,1:24:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We admitted we were powerless,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.24,1:24:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,powerless over alcohol or drugs,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.24,1:24:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,as the case may be.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.34,1:24:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And the minute,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.34,1:24:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,when you come out of denial,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.53,1:24:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,when you come out of this denial,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.53,1:24:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and the reversed energy field,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.53,1:24:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,which is bringing destruction into the person's life,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.53,1:24:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the admission that I'm powerless over alcohol or drugs
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.98,1:24:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is the first statement of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.98,1:24:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And what it does is reverse the energy field
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.01,1:24:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and bring into the person's life,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.01,1:24:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,through empowerment,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.04,1:24:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the first reaction you see,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.04,1:24:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,in fact, the external representation of that empowerment,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.04,1:24:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is that they find themselves now in an energy field of 500 and over.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.04,1:24:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So they become empowered then.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.78,1:24:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So the first step of Alcoholics Anonymous then,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.78,1:24:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,because it tells the truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.78,1:24:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,reverses the energy field, the admission,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.78,1:24:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm powerless over drugs and alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.42,1:25:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The second step of Alcoholics Anonymous then,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.42,1:25:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, deepens that statement of truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.58,1:25:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The awareness that some power
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.58,1:25:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,greater than myself
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.58,1:25:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,is necessary to return me to sanity.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.70,1:25:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Insanity, in that definition,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.70,1:25:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,being anything in these destructive energy states,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.70,1:25:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,those denials of the truth then,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.70,1:25:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and languaged as insanity.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.70,1:25:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Something greater than myself is necessary
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.70,1:25:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to turn this whole field around.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.70,1:25:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Something greater than myself,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.70,1:25:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and by that they're talking about the small self.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.70,1:25:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Something outside of,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.70,1:25:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and more powerful than the ego,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.70,1:25:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to be necessary to conquer the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.96,1:25:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Something greater than what is in the box.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.96,1:25:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that is outside of the box.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.50,1:25:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Some lever that has the power
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.50,1:25:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to lift that which is in the box.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.50,1:25:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Intuitive awareness that I, of my own self,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.50,1:26:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,this self here, unaided,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.50,1:26:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,do then have the power to overcome
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.50,1:26:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the attraction of an energy field of that power.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.50,1:26:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The attraction to return to that state of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.50,1:26:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is so powerful that it requires something
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.50,1:26:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of equal power to neutralize it and to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.50,1:26:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an admission of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.50,1:26:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So the second step then,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.58,1:26:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,furthers and deepens the commitment to the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.81,1:26:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and brings the person face to face with the third step.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.77,1:26:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to turn over
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.77,1:26:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,my life and my will
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.77,1:26:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to God as I understand him,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.77,1:26:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to something greater than myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.77,1:26:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The turning over,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.77,1:26:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the surrender.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.77,1:26:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So the step of surrender then,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.15,1:26:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,coming out of the pain and the suffering
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.41,1:26:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,of the descents into hell,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.41,1:26:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,because these lower states are really
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.95,1:26:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,approaching states of hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.53,1:27:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The surrender, the letting go then,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.53,1:27:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and the turning over of one's life
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.53,1:27:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to something greater than oneself,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.53,1:27:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that moves one up into this energy field
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.53,1:27:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of the self-help groups of the 500 energy fields.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.53,1:27:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That surrender, that I myself cannot do it,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.17,1:27:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is what brings about eventually the salvation
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.17,1:27:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,because it opens the space for something
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.17,1:27:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,greater than oneself to come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.17,1:27:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It opens the space for the grace of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.17,1:27:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And so people who recover from the addictions
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.17,1:27:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,will say that it happened to them
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.52,1:27:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,as the grace of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.52,1:27:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not something that the ego did
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.52,1:27:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of its own doingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.52,1:27:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That it was something outside
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.52,1:27:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which I thought I was
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.52,1:27:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that transformed my life
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.52,1:27:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and the desire to drink disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.52,1:27:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,which is what exactly happened
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.52,1:27:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to my own personal experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.52,1:27:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Being an atheist at the time,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.52,1:27:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,an atheist for some 20 years,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.52,1:27:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and a devoted atheist,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.65,1:27:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,a devout atheist,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.65,1:27:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,not a casual cocktail lounge atheist,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.65,1:28:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but I mean I was an atheist,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.65,1:28:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because I was committed to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.68,1:28:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll get to that when we talk about
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.68,1:28:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the various conceptualizations of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.87,1:28:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My own dedication to the truth told me
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.87,1:28:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that how it was conceived was false.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.32,1:28:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And so anyway,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.32,1:28:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that preoccupation with God
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.32,1:28:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,has gone on throughout my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.32,1:28:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was a child,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.32,1:28:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a devoted religionist.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.32,1:28:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I became a devoted atheist.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.32,1:28:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And then in a moment
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.35,1:28:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,when I myself hit bottom
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.35,1:28:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,at a great depth and great despair
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.35,1:28:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and out of utter hopelessness,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.35,1:28:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked God,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.64,1:28:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,if there was such an entity
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.64,1:28:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in the universe to help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.64,1:28:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hold my breath,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.86,1:28:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,not thinking that there was any such item.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.86,1:28:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So the denial broke down,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.86,1:28:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the arrogance of the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.86,1:28:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The arrogance of the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.86,1:28:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a left-brained person,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.86,1:28:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't conceive that there was anything
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.86,1:29:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,other than intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.86,1:29:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that intelligence was God,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.86,1:29:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that man through his intelligence
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.86,1:29:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,would solve all his problems,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.86,1:29:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,through his intellect.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.86,1:29:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I worshipped the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.86,1:29:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I was baptized by the God of the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.86,1:29:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Reason, you know, Thomas Paine's age,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.86,1:29:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,reason really hit me when I was like 15 or 16
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.86,1:29:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,when I became an atheist.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.27,1:29:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Reason and the intellect,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.27,1:29:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the left brain, the intellect,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.27,1:29:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the IQ, I was born with a good IQ.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.27,1:29:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought IQ,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.62,1:29:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,intelligence, reason, science,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.62,1:29:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that was going to solve all man's dilemmas.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.62,1:29:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.30,1:29:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Following my best reasoning,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.30,1:29:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I found myself at death's door,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.30,1:29:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,having been given up as hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.30,1:29:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, having followed my own best reasoning,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.30,1:29:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I found myself
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.30,1:29:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,at the very bottom of the box,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.30,1:29:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,very close to death.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.30,1:29:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And suicide, by the way,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.30,1:29:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at a minus 50.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.26,1:29:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero, it's below zero,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.26,1:29:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it's in the lower beginnings of hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.38,1:29:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So I had a reversed energy field of minus 50.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.38,1:30:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So from that state,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.90,1:30:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the atheist asked if there was something
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.90,1:30:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,greater than himself in the universe
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.90,1:30:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and totally surrendered
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.90,1:30:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and committed himself to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.02,1:30:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever there was.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.02,1:30:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That emptiness, it seemed to me that nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.02,1:30:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And walked off the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.02,1:30:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And in that instant,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.54,1:30:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,in that instant,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.54,1:30:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,was an enormous transformation.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.54,1:30:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And the person that had been
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.54,1:30:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,no longer existed.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.54,1:30:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And instead,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.54,1:30:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,stood in the presence of the infinite,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.82,1:30:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the infiniteness of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.82,1:30:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That which had infinite power.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.82,1:30:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And it ran me.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.59,1:30:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It ran whatever this body did
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.59,1:30:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,or whatever it said,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.72,1:30:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,what it thought, what went on with it,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.72,1:30:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,was run by that
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.78,1:30:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,infinite presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.78,1:30:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So from the very bottom of the box,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.88,1:30:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you can break out of the box
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.88,1:30:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,through that
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.88,1:30:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,experience of surrender.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.88,1:30:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the third step,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.88,1:30:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,which creates the space
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.98,1:31:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,for that which by grace
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.98,1:31:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,takes the place of that which we were.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.98,1:31:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a question?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.69,1:31:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What she asks is,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.69,1:31:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is grace available to anyone who asks for it?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.69,1:31:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It is only by asking for it
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.69,1:31:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that we create the space.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.01,1:31:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because of the law of free will.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.01,1:31:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So when we ask for it,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.33,1:31:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,we create the space,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.33,1:31:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the possibility
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.33,1:31:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,for it to happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.33,1:31:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only through the surrender
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.33,1:31:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that such an incredible experience
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.33,1:31:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,could have occurred.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.32,1:31:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill Wilson said that
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.32,1:31:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,AA is the language of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.32,1:31:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,AA is the language of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.32,1:31:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That heart being.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.32,1:31:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So when we talk about that chakra,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.28,1:31:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy field of the heart,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.28,1:31:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,see these are the laws
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.28,1:31:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of the lower energy fields,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.28,1:31:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the lower chakras,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.28,1:32:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you move up through the solar plexus
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.31,1:32:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you move into the heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.31,1:32:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So Bill Wilson said AA
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.31,1:32:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is the language of the heart,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.31,1:32:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,not of the intellect,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.92,1:32:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,not of the head,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.92,1:32:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,not of the mind with a small m,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.92,1:32:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but that of one's own inner experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.66,1:32:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So the third step then opens
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.66,1:32:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the way for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.66,1:32:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Through that despair,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.66,1:32:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the arrogance of the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.69,1:32:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,finally lets go.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.69,1:32:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the addiction,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.69,1:32:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a total transformation.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.72,1:32:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The transformation may not be complete
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.72,1:32:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and include the whole personality,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.72,1:32:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,obviously,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.72,1:32:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's the reason for the 12 steps.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.72,1:32:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least in one area
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.72,1:32:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,there has been complete and absolute
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.72,1:32:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and total surrender
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.72,1:32:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and its replacement by grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.39,1:32:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The fourth step then says
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.39,1:32:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that we took a fearless moral inventory.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.39,1:32:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So the fourth step then says
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.39,1:32:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,what we did was we looked in the box,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.39,1:32:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,we looked in our box
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.39,1:32:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,in our own particular case.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.39,1:33:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And after looking in the box
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.22,1:33:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to see what's in there in our own particular case,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.22,1:33:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,for one thing we discovered
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.22,1:33:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,if we move on to the fifth step
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.22,1:33:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that what's in our box is no different
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.22,1:33:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,than what's in everybody else's box,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.22,1:33:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego being the same in everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.38,1:33:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego is really the same
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.38,1:33:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in its design, in its overall
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.38,1:33:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,way of being in everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.38,1:33:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So that whatever we find within our own
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.38,1:33:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,personal experience really falls
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.38,1:33:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere within the box.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.38,1:33:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore the fifth step
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.51,1:33:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,says we admitted
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.74,1:33:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to God and to ourselves
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.74,1:33:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and to another human
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.74,1:33:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,being the exact
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.77,1:33:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,nature of what we discovered
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.77,1:33:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,within ourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.12,1:33:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In admitting it to
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.12,1:33:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,myself, in admitting it
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.12,1:33:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to God and to another fellow human being
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.12,1:33:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,what I've done now is reversed the
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.12,1:33:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,energy field on it, taken the charge
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.12,1:33:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,off it, removed its
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.41,1:33:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,power to corrode and
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.41,1:33:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,destroy. When I look
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.70,1:33:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,at a thing, when I let go of the deny
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.70,1:34:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,when I'm willing to handle whatever
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.70,1:34:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,pain comes up in the looking at it,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.70,1:34:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to heal it,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.89,1:34:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to ask that it be healed,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.11,1:34:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to share it with another human being
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.11,1:34:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is part of the whole process
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.11,1:34:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of healing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.30,1:34:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that which is held in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.30,1:34:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and never shared has by
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.30,1:34:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that virtue of that power
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.30,1:34:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to corrode. The minute it's shared
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.53,1:34:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,with another human being it's now held
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.53,1:34:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,in a different way, it's held in a different
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.53,1:34:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,context, it's transformed into a shared
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.53,1:34:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,communication and
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.72,1:34:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,its capacity to destroy has not
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.72,1:34:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,been removed. So the event
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.72,1:34:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in one's life, instead
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.72,1:34:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,of lying awake at night
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.72,1:34:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,hating in self-hatred, that
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.72,1:34:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,self-hatred which comes out the bottom
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.72,1:34:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,of the box, maybe
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.72,1:34:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,what's left of it is a mild
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.72,1:34:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,regret, a mild regret.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.72,1:34:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what Bill Wilson said.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.61,1:34:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that whatever you've done in your life
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.61,1:34:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,at best, the way to hold
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.90,1:34:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it now is with a decent regret.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.90,1:34:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A decent regret.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.99,1:35:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,To replace that horrible
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.99,1:35:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,intense self-hatred and depression
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.99,1:35:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and contempt, self-contempt
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.99,1:35:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,which leads to the actual
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.99,1:35:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,seeking out of destruction.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.99,1:35:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that the process coming out of the box
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.99,1:35:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is the
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.02,1:35:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,willful, lethal satisfaction
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.02,1:35:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,out of one's own
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.02,1:35:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,destruction. Because an energy
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.02,1:35:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,fuel that reverses now seeks
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.02,1:35:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,its own destruction. And so
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.18,1:35:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you tell the person that they're killing
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.18,1:35:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,themselves with drugs
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.18,1:35:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and you think you're going to scare them out of it
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.18,1:35:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you're merely appealing to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.18,1:35:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet I am. Love it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.18,1:35:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Love it. Love it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.28,1:35:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see how you're playing right
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.28,1:35:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,into the person's self-destruction.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.28,1:35:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,To say if you keep on drinking
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.28,1:35:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,your liver is going to fail.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.28,1:35:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. The people
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.28,1:35:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,got an unconscious satisfaction
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.28,1:35:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,out of that
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.60,1:35:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,self-destruction. There was a purpose in it
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.60,1:35:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was the only way they could see to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.60,1:35:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In this energy field here
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.60,1:35:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,self-destruction is obviously
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.60,1:36:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,what is appealing to you and attractive.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.60,1:36:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the fifth step
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.60,1:36:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,then removes the appeal and the
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.60,1:36:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,attractiveness of that which is
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.60,1:36:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,destructive. It is no longer
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.73,1:36:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,appealing.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.73,1:36:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That leads us to the sixth through
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.92,1:36:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the ninth steps, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.92,1:36:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Having looked at what's in the
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.92,1:36:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,box and having seen what its
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.92,1:36:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,nature is now and admitted
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.92,1:36:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it to ourself and changed the charge
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.92,1:36:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,on that through sharing
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.92,1:36:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it and asking God's forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.92,1:36:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and help with it. Then what we
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.27,1:36:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,do is we move back into the world
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.27,1:36:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,into a step of action. We
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.27,1:36:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,moved up in the box to appropriate
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.27,1:36:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,action and not through action
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.27,1:36:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to try and undo what damage
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.27,1:36:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,we can. To repair
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.27,1:36:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever fences that we
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.27,1:36:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,can repair. To
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.27,1:36:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,tell people that we're sorry for how we
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.27,1:36:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,were. To
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.27,1:36:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,ask for their forgiveness. To
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.27,1:36:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,pay up the bills that we didn't pay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.46,1:36:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, to give
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.07,1:36:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the employer a good day's work.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.07,1:37:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And we always suggest that people
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.30,1:37:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,do that with the help of a sponsor.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.30,1:37:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully that their wisdom will keep
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.30,1:37:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,people from impetuously
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.62,1:37:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,acting out in a self-destructive
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.62,1:37:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,way. But the best way
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.62,1:37:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to repay your boss
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.62,1:37:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,is not to tell them that you've been
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.62,1:37:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,embezzling
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.62,1:37:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the cash box the last ten years, which
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.62,1:37:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,make it an M.I.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.62,1:37:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Raider calling the police.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.62,1:37:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The best way to repay him would be to give him
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.62,1:37:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,an honest day's work for a change.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.62,1:37:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And the best
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.62,1:37:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,way to heal and repair
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.62,1:37:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,your relationship is to put
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.62,1:37:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the best that you can into it to make that
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.62,1:37:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,relationship work. So to try
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.16,1:37:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to undo the damage that came out of
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.16,1:37:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the past then. So that
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.16,1:37:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that inner searching into
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.16,1:37:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,what was wrong within then
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.16,1:37:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes reflected back in the world
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.16,1:37:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in those steps six through nine.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.57,1:37:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The tenth step then says
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.57,1:37:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that we began to, we
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.57,1:37:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,made a habit of this. In other words,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.57,1:37:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it became our way of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.57,1:38:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-purification.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.57,1:38:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the drugs took us to the bottom of
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.57,1:38:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the box and now through the
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.57,1:38:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual program of the
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.57,1:38:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,twelve steps we're moving back up through the
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.57,1:38:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,box. So the tenth step said
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.66,1:38:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that this became our way of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.66,1:38:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the way we became in
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.66,1:38:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the world. That the best of
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.05,1:38:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,our knowledge as we became aware
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.05,1:38:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,as we became aware
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.05,1:38:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which was wrong within us
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.05,1:38:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,we sought to correct it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.05,1:38:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that commitment to self-correction
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.05,1:38:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to spiritual growth
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.05,1:38:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to becoming more conscious then
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.05,1:38:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes part of the way of life
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.05,1:38:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that comes out of this experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.05,1:38:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The eleventh step
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.85,1:38:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is an interesting one. The eleventh
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.20,1:38:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,step says, sought through
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.74,1:38:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,prayer and meditation
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.81,1:38:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to increase our conscious contact
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.81,1:38:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,with God as we understood Him.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.81,1:38:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a very interesting statement
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.81,1:38:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,when you look at it. It says
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.81,1:38:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,sought through prayer and meditation
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.81,1:38:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to increase
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.10,1:38:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,our conscious contact with God.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.10,1:39:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,To increase our contact with
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.10,1:39:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,God as we understood Him.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.19,1:39:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So what that is saying then is
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.19,1:39:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,by the time you've gone through
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.19,1:39:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,steps one through ten
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.19,1:39:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,eleven doesn't say try to
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.19,1:39:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,establish contact with some
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.19,1:39:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,power greater than myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.19,1:39:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Eleven says increase
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.19,1:39:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that which has already happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.19,1:39:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So that
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.35,1:39:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,whole process of surrender
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.35,1:39:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the opening of the energy fuels
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.35,1:39:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience of some
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.35,1:39:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,inner grace, the spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.74,1:39:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,growth that comes out of that
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.74,1:39:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens is you reconnect within yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.74,1:39:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,with something that is rock
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.74,1:39:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,like. See that which is love
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.74,1:39:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is divine
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.74,1:39:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is not different than love.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.74,1:39:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.74,1:39:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I always tell people
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.77,1:39:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,in these programs who
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.77,1:39:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,have trouble with the God aspect
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.77,1:39:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,of it to forget about the God aspect
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.77,1:39:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,of it and instead commit themselves
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.77,1:39:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to this energy fuel called
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.77,1:39:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,love and to these states up here
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.77,1:39:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,which are called compassion
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.77,1:40:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to commit oneself to truth
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.73,1:40:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to love and to compassion.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.76,1:40:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about the God aspect
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.76,1:40:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,because what happens as time goes
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.76,1:40:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,on is you feel that
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.76,1:40:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,rock like interconnectedness
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.76,1:40:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and so you'll hear people
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.76,1:40:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,who have been sober for some time
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.95,1:40:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,will talk about their sobriety
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.95,1:40:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,as though it was some very
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.95,1:40:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,wonderful and positive
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.30,1:40:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,attribute
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.43,1:40:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and they will guard that with their life.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.43,1:40:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What these people seemed to have
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.43,1:40:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,was something that was so great
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.43,1:40:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that they would go to any lengths to guard it
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.43,1:40:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and to protect it. Something of
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.43,1:40:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,great significance that they had something
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.43,1:40:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,over and beyond that which they had gotten out of
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.43,1:40:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,alcohol and drugs in the first place
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.43,1:40:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,otherwise they would still be back in alcohol
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.43,1:40:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and drugs. Something of a greater
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.43,1:40:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,dimension had come into their life
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.43,1:40:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was within them.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.50,1:40:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The kingdom of God is experienced
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.50,1:40:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,within and so that
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.78,1:40:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,rock like reconnection with that which
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.78,1:40:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,they had sought in the beginning
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.78,1:40:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,now was happening. So step 11
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.78,1:41:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,then merely said
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.82,1:41:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that there was a desire
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.85,1:41:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,now and following through
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.85,1:41:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,on how to increase the power of that
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.85,1:41:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,connectedness with something that
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.85,1:41:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,had come back within the self.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.85,1:41:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Some re-experiencing of truth
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.85,1:41:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,had recurred
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.17,1:41:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and that brought them to the 12th step
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.17,1:41:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and the 12th step then explains
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.17,1:41:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,what the whole process
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.17,1:41:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of addiction is about.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.17,1:41:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Step 12 says
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.17,1:41:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,having become conscious as a result
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.17,1:41:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of this total addictive experience
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.17,1:41:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of having become addicted, having
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.17,1:41:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,surrendered, having hit bottom
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.17,1:41:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,having turned around, having
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.17,1:41:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,gone through a process of spiritual purification
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.17,1:41:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and the wording of it
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.97,1:41:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is having had a spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.97,1:41:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,awakening as a result
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.97,1:41:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,of this whole experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.97,1:41:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So now we see what the process
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.64,1:41:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of addiction is all about. It is a
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.64,1:41:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,movement in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.64,1:41:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it is a one way street
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.64,1:41:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,a one way commitment because
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.64,1:41:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,once your own consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.64,1:42:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,has picked addiction as
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.64,1:42:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the way to becoming conscious
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.64,1:42:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as the way to becoming spiritually aware
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.64,1:42:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no backing up
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.64,1:42:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no changing of one's mind
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.64,1:42:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you cannot join this pathway
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.74,1:42:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and then leave it and join some other pathway
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.74,1:42:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and commit to some other church
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.25,1:42:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and then go to unity for a while
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.25,1:42:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and then do the course of miracles
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.25,1:42:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,move around through one thing and another
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.25,1:42:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you are now committed
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.25,1:42:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to a one way street
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.25,1:42:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,walking a razor's edge because
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.25,1:42:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,there isn't enough room on it
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.60,1:42:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to turn around and go back.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.00,1:42:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Addiction is a one way street
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.00,1:42:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it is a total confront with
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.00,1:42:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the absolute necessity
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.00,1:42:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of becoming more conscious
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.00,1:42:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to live
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.00,1:42:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so that the price of life now
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.00,1:42:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,itself is that
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.00,1:42:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,one has to become more conscious
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.00,1:42:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is the whole purpose
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.00,1:42:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in consciousness then of
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.00,1:42:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the pathway so it is really
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.00,1:42:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,a pathway
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.06,1:43:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,a consciousness pathway
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.06,1:43:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole purpose of addiction then is
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.06,1:43:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it is a way in which
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.06,1:43:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,one is forced
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.13,1:43:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,despite oneself to become conscious
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.13,1:43:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to own the truth about oneself
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.13,1:43:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to a much greater degree
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.13,1:43:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,or one dies
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.13,1:43:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,in the process and therefore
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.13,1:43:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it is a very powerful
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.16,1:43:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,commitment it is really in a way
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.16,1:43:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,a long shot because
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.16,1:43:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you either make it you either become more conscious
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.16,1:43:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,or you go out the bottom of the box
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.16,1:43:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and at the villa they talk about
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.16,1:43:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,going out the bottom of the box
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.16,1:43:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and this last week somebody else went out the bottom of the box
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.16,1:43:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,because the statistics
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.16,1:43:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,are not all that great
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.15,1:43:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,out of 10 million alcoholics
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.15,1:43:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,there is 500,000 sober
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.15,1:43:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,roughly one out of 20
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.15,1:43:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,means that it is a long shot
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.15,1:43:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in which maybe one out of 20
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.15,1:43:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,will own the truth about themselves
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.15,1:43:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to a sufficient degree
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.28,1:43:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that their life will return to them
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.28,1:43:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so the 12th step
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.50,1:43:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,then gives away what the purpose
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.50,1:44:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole purpose
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.50,1:44:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the end the goal of addiction
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.50,1:44:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is and that is to become more conscious
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.50,1:44:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,see you can't change
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.62,1:44:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,your mind once you are an addicted
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.62,1:44:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,person you cannot become
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.62,1:44:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,unaddicted once you have
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.62,1:44:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,experienced this energy state
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.62,1:44:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no way to remove
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.62,1:44:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,it from ones memory
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.66,1:44:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,ones alignment with the returning
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.66,1:44:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to that state the desire to
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.66,1:44:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,return to that state
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.20,1:44:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,its impossible to replace that state
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.20,1:44:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,with anything else because anything else
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.20,1:44:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is of a much lesser degree
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.20,1:44:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,a much lesser degree
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.20,1:44:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the desire to return to that state
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.80,1:44:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,then becomes that which
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.80,1:44:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,runs the person
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.31,1:44:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,so we tell people
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.31,1:44:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,at the villa that
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.31,1:44:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,what it is you sought you don't have to be ashamed of
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.31,1:44:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,what you sought
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.31,1:44:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,was the same thing that all the saints
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.31,1:44:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and everyone else has sought
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.31,1:44:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to experience that great
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.44,1:44:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,state within oneself
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.44,1:45:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the presence within
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.44,1:45:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.14,1:45:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,what you have to know is that
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.14,1:45:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,what's wrong with drugs is
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.14,1:45:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't work
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.30,1:45:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not because they're wrong
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.30,1:45:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not because they're destructive
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.30,1:45:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just that they do not work that's all
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.30,1:45:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,they work up to a certain point
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.37,1:45:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and then once the energy fuel reverses
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.37,1:45:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,they do not work so the reason to give up drugs
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.37,1:45:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and alcohol is frankly
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.37,1:45:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that they no longer work
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.46,1:45:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't work
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.46,1:45:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and now that you know what it is you're addicted to
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.46,1:45:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to change your direction at all
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.46,1:45:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,your goal before
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.46,1:45:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,what you sought was to experience
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.46,1:45:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,this higher energy state
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.46,1:45:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so you don't have to change your direction
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.46,1:45:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you only have to change the means of getting there
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.46,1:45:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you only have to change
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.46,1:45:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the means of getting there
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.46,1:45:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so that now you own it yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.46,1:45:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so that as you return
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.46,1:45:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to that state
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.46,1:45:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it's because of what you are
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.46,1:45:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it is not something out there
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.46,1:45:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it's merely the awareness of what you are
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.46,1:45:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so that
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.46,1:46:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that state now stems and comes from
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.46,1:46:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,within yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.67,1:46:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,as people go through a confront
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.67,1:46:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you know a confront with the facts
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.67,1:46:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,about their addiction they go through these
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.67,1:46:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,various experiences
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.67,1:46:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,they very often come in
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.67,1:46:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,in the bottom state of despondency
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.67,1:46:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and everybody pours
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.67,1:46:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,energy into them in which state
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.67,1:46:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,often they start to cry
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.67,1:46:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,at the grief over their experience
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.67,1:46:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to find yourself committed
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.67,1:46:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to find yourself at the bottom of the box
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.67,1:46:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to find that all that you have valued
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.67,1:46:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,has been lost and taken away
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.67,1:46:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the person goes into grief
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.67,1:46:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,grief over the realization
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.67,1:46:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that they are addicted
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.67,1:46:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,grief over the realization that they have
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.67,1:46:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,what seems to them
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.12,1:46:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is an impossible problem
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.12,1:46:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and out of that comes the fear
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.12,1:46:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to help the person through the fear
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.12,1:46:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of what the consequences of this addiction are
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.12,1:46:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and move them up into desiring
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.12,1:46:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,something better for themselves
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.12,1:46:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to move themselves
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.18,1:47:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to move them up into anger
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.18,1:47:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to use that anger to move them into pride
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.18,1:47:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to move them into courage
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.18,1:47:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and so the person can be moved
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.18,1:47:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the bottom of the box
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.25,1:47:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and we will see later
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.25,1:47:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,a social phenomena which demonstrates
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.25,1:47:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,these principles extremely well
